# Environment variables for route-service are in the monorepo root .env.example
# See: ../.env.example
#
# Relevant vars for this service:
#   NODE_ENV, LOG_LEVEL, CORS_ORIGINS
#   FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON
#   ROUTE_SERVICE_PORT (default: 4003)
#   GOOGLE_MAPS_DIRECTIONS_KEY — server-only key for the Directions API proxy
#     (optional; when absent, /polyline and /directions return [])
#     This key NEVER goes to the client. Create a separate restricted key in
#     Google Cloud Console → restrict to "IP addresses" (your server IPs).
